'''Dagannoth Rex''' is the [[Melee]]-based [[Dagannoth King]] found in the depths of the [[Waterbirth Island Dungeon]], along with fellow Dagannoth Kings, [[Dagannoth Supreme]] and [[Dagannoth Prime]]. Rex is the only monster to drop the [[Berserker ring|Berserker]] and [[Warrior ring]]s, which can become best-in-slot rings for Strength and Slash after being imbued at the [[Nightmare Zone]]. He, along with the other Dagannoth Kings, can also drop the rare [[dragon axe]].

